\" |169-206\n| colspan=\"2\" |38\n|-\n|5\n|\"Kokoro no Chizu\"\n|BOYSTYLE\n| colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"18\" |N/A (Not dubbed)\n| colspan=\"2\" |207-263\n| colspan=\"2\" |57\n|-\n|6\n|\"Brand New World\"\n|[[D-51]]\n| colspan=\"2\" |264-278\n| colspan=\"2\" |15\n|-\n|7\n|\"We Are! (Straw Hat Pirates Version)\"\n|Cast of the Straw Hat Pirates\n|279-283\n|279-325\n|5\n|47\n|-\n|8\n|[[Dame/Crazy Rainbow|\"Crazy Rainbow\"]]\n|[[Tackey and Tsubasa]]\n|284-325\n|Not licensed\n|42\n| -\n|-\n|9\n|\"Jungle P\"\n|5050\n|326-372\n|326-458\n|47\n|133\n|-\n|10\n|\"We Are! (Remix)\"\n|[[TVXQ]]\n|373-394\n| rowspan=\"3\" |Not licensed\n|22\n| rowspan=\"3\" | -\n|-\n|11\n|[[Share the World / We Are!|\"Share the World!\"]]\n|[[TVXQ]]\n|395-425\n|31\n|-\n|12\n|\"Kaze o Sagashite\"\n|[[Mari Yaguchi|Yaguchi Mari]], Straw Hats cast\n|426-458\n|33\n|-\n|13\n|\"One day\"\n|THE ROOTLESS\n| colspan=\"2\" |459-492\n| colspan=\"2\" |34\n|-\n|14\n|[[Naked/Fight Together/Tempest|\"Fight Together\"]]\n|[[Namie Amuro]]\n| colspan=\"2\" |493-516\n| colspan=\"2\" |24\n|-\n|15\n|\"We Go!\"\n|[[Hiroshi Kitadani]]\n|517-590\n|517-628\n|72\n|111\n|-\n|16\n|\"Hands Up!\"\n|Kota Shinzato\n|591-628\n|Not licensed\n|38\n| -\n|-\n|17\n|\"Wake up!\"\n|[[AAA (band)|AAA]]\n| colspan=\"2\" |629-686\n| colspan=\"2\" |58\n|-\n|18\n|\"Hard Knock Days\"\n|[[Generations from Exile Tribe]]\n| colspan=\"2\" |687-746\n| colspan=\"2\" |60\n|-\n|19\n|\"We Can!\"\n|Hiroshi Kitadani and Kishidan\n| colspan=\"2\" |747-806\n| colspan=\"2\" |60\n|-\n|20\n|\"Hope\"\n|[[Namie Amuro]]\n| colspan=\"2\" |807-855\n| colspan=\"2\" |49\n|-\n|21\n|\"Super Powers\"\n|[[V6 (band)|V6]]\n| colspan=\"2\" |856-891\n| colspan=\"2\" |36\n|-\n|22\n|\"OVER THE TOP\"\n|[[Hiroshi Kitadani]] and\n[[Kohei Tanaka (composer)|Kohei Tanaka]] (music)\n| colspan=\"2\" |892-present\n| colspan=\"2\" |TBD\n|}\n\n;Alternates\n# \"One Piece Rap\" (4Kids)\n#* Version 1: (Episodes 1-29)\n#* Version 2: (Episodes 30-59) (inclusion of Sanji and Usopp in the lyrics)\n